<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='217:244'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='244:252'>詩本義卷第四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='252:263'>　　　　　　歐陽氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='263:272'>　　　　叔于田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='272:294'>論曰叔于田之義至簡而明毛鄭於飲酒服馬無所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='294:316'>解說而謂巷無居人者國人注心於叔似如無人處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='316:338'>不惟其說迂踈且與下二章飲酒服馬文義不類以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='338:356'>此知非詩人本意也雖爲小失不可不正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='356:378'>本義曰詩人言大叔得衆國人愛之以謂叔出于田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='378:400'>則所居之巷若無人矣非實無人雖有而不如叔之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='400:422'>羙且仁也其二章又言叔出則巷無可共飲酒之人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='422:449'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='449:471'>矣雖有而不如叔之羙且好也其三章又言叔出則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='471:493'>巷無能服馬之人矣雖有而不如叔之羙且武也皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='493:499'>愛之之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='499:507'>　　　　羔裘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='507:529'>論曰羔裘晏兮三英粲兮毛鄭皆以三英爲三德者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='529:551'>本無所據蓋旁取書之三德曲爲附麗爾六經所在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='551:573'>三數甚多苟可曲以附麗則何說不可據詩三章皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='573:595'>上兩言述羔裘之羙下兩言稱其人之善其一章曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='595:617'>羔裘如濡洵直且侯者言此裘潤澤信可以爲君朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='617:639'>服洵信也至其下言則稱其人曰彼其之子守命不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='639:666'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='666:688'>變也其二章曰羔裘豹餙孔武有力言裘所以用豹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='688:710'>爲餙者以豹有武力之獸也故其下言稱其人云彼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='710:732'>其之子邦之司直者謂服以武力之獸爲飾而彼剛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='732:754'>彊正直之人稱其服爾其三章曰羔裘晏兮三英粲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='754:776'>兮亦當是述羔裘之羙其下言始云彼其之子邦之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='776:798'>彦兮者謂稱其服也英羙也粲衣服鮮明貌但三英</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='798:816'>失其義不知其爲何物爾故闕其所未詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='816:826'>　　　　女曰雞鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='826:848'>論曰女曰雞鳴士曰昩旦是詩人述夫婦相與語爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='848:870'>其終篇皆是夫婦相語之事蓋言古之賢夫婦相語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='870:897'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='897:919'>者如此所以見其妻之不以色取愛於其夫而夫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='919:941'>於其妻不說其色而内相勉勵以成其賢也而鄭氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='941:963'>於其卒章知子之来之以爲子者是異國之賓客又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='963:985'>言豫儲珩璜雜佩又云雖無此物猶言之以致意皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='985:1007'>非詩文所有委曲生意而失詩本義且旣解卒章以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1007:1029'>此又因以冝言飲酒與子偕老亦爲賓客斯又泥而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1029:1051'>不通者也今徧考詩諸風言偕老者多矣皆爲夫婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1051:1073'>之言也且賓客一時相接豈有偕老之理是殊不近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1073:1087'>人情以此求詩何由得詩之義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1087:1109'>本義曰詩人刺時好色而不說德乃陳古賢夫婦相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1109:1136'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1136:1158'>警勵以勤生之語謂婦勉其夫早起徃取鳬鴈以爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1158:1180'>具飲酒歸以相樂御其琴瑟樂而不淫以相期於偕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1180:1202'>老凢云子者皆婦謂其夫也其卒章又言知子之来</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1202:1224'>相和好者當有以贈報之以勉其夫不獨厚於室家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1224:1246'>又當尊賢友善而因物以結之此所謂說德而不好</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1246:1256'>色以刺時之不然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1256:1271'>　　　　有女同車　山有扶蘇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1271:1293'>論曰女有同車序言刺忽不昏於齊卒以無大國之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1293:1315'>助至於見逐今考本篇了無此語若於山有扶蘇義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1315:1337'>則有之山有扶蘇序言刺忽所羙非羙考其本篇亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1337:1364'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1364:1386'>無其語若於有女同車義則有之二篇相次疑其戰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1386:1408'>國秦漢之際六經焚㓕詩以諷誦相傳易爲差失漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1408:1429'>興承其訛謬不能考正遂以至今然不知魯韓齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1429:1451'>三家之義又爲何說也今移其序文附二篇之首則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1451:1473'>詩義煥然不求自得定本有女同車刺忽也所羙非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1473:1495'>羙然山有扶蘇刺忽也鄭人刺忽之不昏于齊太子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1495:1517'>忽甞有功于齊齊侯請妻之齊女賢而不取卒以無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1517:1539'>大國之助至于見逐故國人刺之毛鄭之說與子之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1539:1549'>本義學者可以擇焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1549:1571'>本義曰有女同車顔如舜華將翺将翔佩玉瓊琚彼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1571:1598'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1598:1620'>羙孟姜洵羙且都云者詩人極陳齊女之羙如此而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1620:1642'>鄭忽不知爲羙反娶於他國是所羙非羙也又曰山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1642:1664'>有扶蘇隰有荷華不見子都乃見狂且云者詩人以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1664:1686'>草木依託山隰皆得茂盛榮華以刺鄭忽不能依託</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1686:1708'>大國以自安全遂斥其君此狂狡之童爾各舉一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1708:1718'>則下章之義不異也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1718:1726'>　　　　褰裳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1726:1748'>論曰褰裳之詩鄭有忽突争國之事思大國来定其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1748:1770'>亂也據詩但怨諸侯不来而箋意謂鄭人不徃義正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1770:1792'>相反此其失也其曰子恵思我褰裳渉溱者謂彼大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1792:1819'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1819:1841'>國有恵然思念我鄭國之亂欲來爲我討正之者非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1841:1863'>道逺而難至但褰其裳行渉溱水而來則至矣言甚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1863:1885'>易而不来爾而鄭謂有大國思我則我揭衣渡水徃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1885:1907'>告以難也且以難告人豈待其思而後徃告亦不以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1907:1929'>難難而不徃也子不我思豈無他人者但言諸侯衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1929:1951'>矣子不我思則當有他國思我者爾詩人假爲此言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1951:1973'>以述鄭怨諸侯不相救卹爾而鄭謂先鄉齊晉宋衛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1973:1995'>後之荆楚者穿鑿之衍說也又曰豈無他士者猶言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1995:2017'>他人爾鄭謂大國之卿當天子之上士者亦拘儒之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2017:2021'>說也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2021:2048'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-5a' );" name="004-5a" class="pb">[004-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2048:2056'>　　　　子衿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2056:2078'>論曰子衿據序但刺鄭人學校不脩爾鄭以學子在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2078:2100'>學中有留者有去者毛又以嗣爲習謂習詩樂又以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2100:2122'>一日不見如三月謂禮樂不可一日而廢苟如其說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2122:2144'>則學校脩而不廢其有去者猶有居者則勸其來學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2144:2166'>然則詩人復何所刺哉鄭謂子寜不嗣音爲責其忘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2166:2188'>已則是矣據詩三章皆是學校廢而生徒分散朋友</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2188:2210'>不復群居不相見而思之辭爾挑逹城闕間日遨遊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2210:2216'>無度者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2216:2226'>　　　　東方之日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2226:2253'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-5b' );" name="004-5b" class="pb">[004-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2253:2275'>論曰東方之日毛鄭皆以喻君而毛謂日出東方人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2275:2297'>君明盛鄭謂其明未融喻君不明東方之月毛鄭皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2297:2319'>以喻臣而毛亦謂月盛於東方鄭又以爲不明以詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2319:2341'>文考之日月非喻君臣毛鄭固皆失之矣至於明不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2341:2363'>明之說二家特相反而日出東方明最盛皆智愚所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2363:2385'>具見而鄭以爲不明者蓋遷就已說爾若毛旣謂日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2385:2407'>月在東方爲君臣盛明則於詩序所謂君臣失道者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2407:2418'>義豈得通此其又失也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2418:2440'>本義曰東方之日日之初升也盖言彼姝之子顔色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2440:2462'>奮然羙盛如日之升也在我室兮履我即兮者相邀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2462:2489'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-6a' );" name="004-6a" class="pb">[004-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2489:2511'>以奔之辭也此述男女淫風但知稱其羙色以相誇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2511:2533'>榮而不顧禮義所謂不能以禮化也下章之義亦然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2533:2541'>　　　　南山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2541:2563'>論曰南山刺齊襄與魯文姜之事毛鄭得之多矣其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2563:2585'>曰葛屨五兩冠緌雙止毛但云葛屨服之賤者冠緌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2585:2607'>服之尊者而不究其說鄭謂葛屨五兩喻文姜與娣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2607:2629'>姪傳姆同處冠緌喻襄公文姜與姪娣傳姆五人爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2629:2651'>竒襄公徃從而雙之詩人之意必不如此然本義已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2651:2661'>失矣故闕其所未詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2661:2669'>　　　　蟋蟀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2669:2696'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2696:2718'>論曰蟋蟀之義簡而易明鄭氏以農功爲詩考序及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2718:2740'>詩但刺僖公不能以禮自娛樂爾初不及農功也國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2740:2762'>君之尊以禮晏樂自有時豈如庻人必待農隙乎鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2762:2784'>惟此爲衍說爾職思其外毛謂禮樂之外鄭謂國外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2784:2806'>至四境鄭又謂職思其憂爲鄰國侵伐之事皆失之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2806:2828'>詩曰蟋蟀在堂者著歳將親而日月之速冝爲樂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2828:2850'>職思其外者謂國君行樂有時使不廢其職事而更</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2850:2872'>思其外爾謂廣爲周慮也一國之政所憂非一事不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2872:2879'>專備侵伐也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2879:2888'>　　　　揚之水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2888:2915'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2915:2937'>論曰詩人本刺昭公封沃而桓叔盛彊而毛鄭謂波</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2937:2959'>流湍疾洗去垢濁使白石鑿鑿然如桓叔除民所患</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2959:2981'>民得有禮義遂如二家之說則是桓叔善治其民非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2981:3003'>其盛彊爲晉患也據序所陳直謂昭公微弱不能制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3003:3025'>桓叔之彊民皆捨弱就彊叛而歸沃爾非謂民知就</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3025:3047'>禮義也使民知就禮義則晉雖弱而不叛也詩王風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3047:3069'>鄭風及此有揚之水三篇其王鄭二篇皆以激揚之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3069:3091'>水力弱不能流移束薪豈獨於此篇謂波流疾湍洗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3091:3113'>去垢濁以意求之當是刺昭公微弱不能制沃與不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3113:3124'>流束薪義同則得之矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3124:3151'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3151:3173'>本義曰激揚之水其力弱不能流移白石以興昭公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3173:3195'>微弱不能制曲沃而桓叔之彊於晉國如白石鑿鑿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3195:3217'>然見於水中爾其民從而樂之則詩文自見毛鄭之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3217:3223'>說亦通也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3223:3231'>　　　　采苓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3231:3253'>論曰毛以采苓爲細事與采葛傳同子於采葛論之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3253:3275'>矣鄭又轉釋細事以爲小行詩人之意明白固不使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3275:3297'>後人湏轉釋而後知也首陽山名人所共見而易知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3297:3319'>者毛以爲幽僻鄭以爲無徴皆失矣至於人之爲言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3319:3341'>苟亦無信舎旃舎旃苟亦無然以文意考之本是爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3341:3368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3368:3390'>一事而鄭分爲二謂人之爲言是稱薦人欲使見進</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3390:3412'>用舎旃舎旃是謗訕人欲使見貶退者考詩之意不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3412:3434'>然也蓋其下文再舉人之爲言而不復舉舎旃舎旃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3434:3442'>者知非二事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3442:3464'>本義曰采苓者積少成多如䜛言漸積以成惑與采</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3464:3486'>葛義同其曰人之爲言苟亦無信舎旃舎旃苟亦無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3486:3508'>然人之爲言胡得焉者戒獻公聞人之言且勿聽信</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3508:3530'>置之且勿以爲然更考其言何所得謂徐察其虗實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3530:3539'>也義止如是而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3539:3547'>　　　　蒹葭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3547:3574'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-8b' );" name="004-8b" class="pb">[004-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3574:3596'>論曰據詩序但言刺襄公未能用周禮爾鄭氏以謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3596:3618'>秦處周之舊土其人被周德教日久襄公新爲諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3618:3640'>未習周之禮法故國人未服按史記秦本紀周幽王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3640:3662'>時西戎犬戎與申侯伐周殺幽王秦襄公將兵救周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3662:3684'>戰有功周避犬戎難東徙洛邑襄公以兵送周平王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3684:3705'>平王封襄公爲諸侯賜之岐以西之地曰戎無道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3705:3727'>侵奪我歧豐之地秦能攻逐戎即有其地襄公於是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3727:3749'>始國與諸侯通十二年伐戎至岐而卒子文公立居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3749:3771'>西垂宮十六年以兵伐戎戎敗走於是遂收周餘民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3771:3793'>有之地至歧又據詩小戎序云襄公備其兵甲以詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3793:3820'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-9a' );" name="004-9a" class="pb">[004-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3820:3842'>西戎西戎方彊而征伐不休但言征伐而不言敗逐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3842:3863'>之以史記及小戎序考之盖自西戎侵奪歧豐周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3863:3885'>遂東遷雖以歧豐賜秦使自攻取而終襄公之世不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3885:3907'>能取之但甞一以兵至岐而卒至文公立十六年始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3907:3929'>逐戎而取歧豐之地然則當詩人作蒹葭之時秦猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3929:3951'>未得周之地鄭氏謂秦處周之舊土大㫖旣乖其餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3951:3961'>失詩本義不論可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3961:3983'>本義曰秦襄公雖未能攻取周地然巳命爲諸侯受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3983:4005'>顯服而不能以周禮變其夷狄之俗故詩人刺之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4005:4027'>詩蒹葭水草蒼蒼然茂盛必待霜降以成其質然後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4027:4054'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0008', 'SBCK', '004-9b' );" name="004-9b" class="pb">[004-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
